title: ScHoolboy Q - Blank Face LP
description:
Blank Face LP is the fourth studio album by American hip hop recording artist Schoolboy Q. The album was released on July 8, 2016, by Top Dawg Entertainment (TDE) and Interscope Records. It is his second project to be released under a major record label to music retailers, following 2014's Oxymoron. The album was preceded by a series of short films; as well as two singles: "Groovy Tony" and "THat Part".

The album features guest appearances from several prominent artists, such as Kanye West, Jadakiss, Tha Dogg Pound, Vince Staples, Lance Skiiiwalker, Anderson .Paak, Candice Pillay, SZA, Miguel and Justine Skye, among others. The production was handled by various high-profile and low profile artist record producers, including Swizz Beatz, Metro Boomin, Southside and Cardo, Atilli as well as frequent collaborators Nez & Rio, The Alchemist, DJ Dahi and members of TDE in-house production team, Digi+Phonics
